{"tid":1920015,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"假的全部是假的 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2020-03-11T07:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T09:16:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f70e2cd4ff585b50d33bfd6230aca377d712f642","tid":1920015,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20200311/20877988/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200311%2F20877988%2F&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=b33065f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25B1%25AA%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200311%2F20877988%2F&h=167d7077\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA/daily/article/20200311/20877988/</a><br />\n<br />\n假的全部是假的 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200311/large/1583822872_d8a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200311%2Flarge%2F1583822872_d8a2.jpg&h=2e432972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這國家的真相都是假的，只有假的才是真相。<br />\n<br />\n國務院副總理孫春蘭到訪武漢一個小區「視察民情」，碰巧遇見一些「志願者」送菜送肉去小區「慰問」居民，解決他們的生活問題，一派「人間有情、武漢加油」的景象。<br />\n<br />\n然後樓上傳來聲音，「假的，假的，全部都是假的。」<br />\n<br />\n這呼聲一發不可收拾，起先只是某戶人家，很快附和者眾，此起彼落，大有「兩岸假的聲不絕，官員已過幾條街」。<br />\n<br />\n原來知得副總理要到訪，這個物業小區的管理員不讓業主下樓表達意見。還要吩咐「霞姨」安排臨時演員扮志願者送愛心菜愛心肉，在副總理面前送溫暖。好讓領導安心，我們一切安好，群眾生活穩健妥當。<br />\n<br />\n造假被當場拆穿，副總理臉上也掛不住，翌日記者會裝模作樣的要求指導組成員徹查事件云云。<br />\n<br />\n這個「假的」呼聲說明甚麼問題？<br />\n<br />\n第一，原來大國的一個區區物業管理員權力可以無法無天，把業主軟禁在屋內！香港人你還敢到內地買樓定居安享晚年嗎？隨時可以讓人扣押封殺。<br />\n<br />\n第二，國內的造假連菜肉米飯這些民生事情都要隱瞞造假，證明這種「假」的基因深入血液，並不限於「政治問題」或重大傷亡問題會「欺上瞞下」。也可以反映出，國內官僚辦不了實事，只能「扮」辦了實事。<br />\n<br />\n第三，這個副總理真的不知真假嗎？真的要靠另一個指導小組去查明真相嗎？「要求徹查」會否也是另一種的「形式主義」？<br />\n<br />\n第四，當連菜肉都要造假，那武漢疫情還有甚麼是真的？我們能相信官方的死亡數字、康復數字、感染數字嗎？如果副總理視察小區都洗太平地到如此乾淨，醫學專家去到武漢當地考察調研，究竟還能看到多少真相？還是欣賞官員的特技效果？<br />\n<br />\n第五，香港官員是否正急起直追？聽電話扮親善大使？當講真話的媒體被政權打壓，以後香港人是否只能在封閉的單位大叫「假的全部都是假的」？ <br />\n<br />\n曾志豪<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"09a560d9d8b3655c32535fee06cab18f552831f5","tid":1920015,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T07:33:03.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾玖期牆紙】 兄弟爬山<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1919455/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1919455/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=7c7e6247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=b80c6138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhongkong_wallpaper%2F&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=7b5a777e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hongkong_wallpaper/</a><br />\nWEB: <a href=\"https://firsthand-news.web.app/wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffirsthand-news.web.app%2Fwallpaper%2F&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=09c3111d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://firsthand-news.web.app/wallpaper/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkDtkZf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c